OUTPUT:
The improved model demonstrates excellent health, cutting MAE by 42.5% from 38.27 to a robust 22.02. The suggested trade is LONG DA / SHORT CURVE, indicating fair value at 109.52 EUR/MWh. Invalidate this view if intraday renewable generation deviates by more than 15% from forecasts or unexpected major plant outages occur. No immediate data quality concerns were highlighted in this run.
